    <h1>What is cuPets? </h1>
    <p>Imagine this scenario, you have your very first pet and you want to share your bundle of joy with the world but
        no one around you has pets. Well, cuPets finds all people that are like you and gives them a platform to talk to
        eachother! Got any questions on how to take care of your new friend? No problem at all! Just message someone
        with a similar pet. Want your pet to become social? Schedule some meetups with your new pet owner friends! The
        sky is the limit on cuPets, so get out there and make some new friends!</p>
    <h2>Who made such an amazing site?</h2>
    <p>Such a miracle that is cuPets only comes once in a lifetime, so give the creators some credit! They're listed below in alphabetical order</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Brandon Carter</li>
        <li>Haleigh Spurlock</li>
        <li>Nelson Escalante</li>
        <li>Yigit Eren Ozgur</li>
    </ul>
